 <h3><center>Terrorism</center></h3>
 
 <p>Terrorism has already taken its worst form in World. It is a great problem for all. It has spread and entered into every vein of this society. Terrorism has been on this earth from time immemorial. The main causes of this may be poverty, social and political instability and the exploitation of the needy by the greedy. Our politicians play a vital role in this sphere. They use the terrorists to dominance. Poverty compells the poor to make a living in this way. Again, most of the educated people in our country are jobless. Some of them start terrorist activities to make money in am easy way. In Bangladesh there is terrorism in the streets and in public places. Even our homes are not safe from their attacks. Kidnapping for ransom and killing for money are everyday routine act. We have to play our sold to stop terrorism at the cost of anything. People should be motivated to get united against the terrorists and government should enforce strict lows to stop terrorist activities from the society.</p>
